Remember place
Discworld ritual help
Remember place


.SH Name
.SP 5 5
Remember place -- Remembers a location to use in other rituals
.EP

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
The ritual "Remember Place" helps you to remember a place
so that you can refer to it in other religious activities.
To cast it successfully, you will need a holy amulet as well
as an item that has been consecrated to your deity to act as
an aide-memoire later on.
.EP

